description:
Wednesday 10/17 - Today on the show we had Dr. Jessica Clemons stop by who spoke about therapy, eradicating the stigma around mental Illness and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Vic Mensa for addressing XXX Tentacion for beating his girl when Vic also beat his girl in the past as well. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
